So basically, `json-tree` includes the dependencies of the dependencies, same as `pipenv graph`, on the other hand, the current `--json` shows the dependencies like `pip freeze`, no deps of deps. 

Intuitively, `json-tree` is a better representation of the bare output of `pipenv graph`.

