@e271828- Here is some example code that works in 2.0.1:

```python
from schematics import Model
from schematics.types import StringType, URLType
from schematics.types import serializable

class Entity(Model):
    parameter = StringType()

    @serializable(type=URLType)
    def entity_url(self):
        if self.parameter is not None and hasattr(self, 'app_data'):
            request = self.app_data.get('request')
            return '{}/{}'.format(request, self.parameter)

e = Entity({'parameter': 'my_endpoint'})
e.app_data = {'request': 'http://example.com'}
e.serialize()
```

